name: Break in space time
description: Falling through the emptiness of my soul I found myself wandering through the solar system, which did not seem like ours. All the planets were quiet, the earth was lifeless and silence penetrated my ears. There was a break in spacetime and the cosmic cold ate my intestines, although I felt the sun shine in my pupils. I do not know where this journey will end but if I die of madness, I hope they remember me as the second man who saw the earth from space without leaving it.
